      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下结构：Client在外部，Entry作为入口，然后Platform子图内部是Entry→Gateway→Orders→Users的链式结构。方向用从左到右（LR）布局对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
